{"tid":1952721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後唔好叫「香港政府」，改口叫「香港軍政府」","createTime":"2020-03-31T18:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T09:49:58.000Z","uid":2962,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d64a3e30f3e3403b7e4d33efd4315a2644ca30b3","tid":1952721,"uid":2962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:37:30.000Z","msg":"相信香港係police state呢樣嘢都應該唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢樣只係大家手足之間心知肚明嘅嘢<br />\n上連登就咁講「好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」係唔足夠㗎！<br />\n<br />\n我哋要諗嘅係，我哋要點樣利用呢個事實，將呢個概念深植喺人心入面，降低政權嘅正當性？<br />\n<br />\n就係改口，以後叫呢個政權做<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「香港軍政府」</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家由細到大聽新聞都會覺得「軍政府」呢個term多數係啲管治好差，成日內戰嘅國家先會有嘅，所以呢個稱呼如果越嚟越多人講，我覺得係可以減低個政府嘅權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，以後跟住我叫，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港軍政府</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cea23cadf6ec11d608a60bd5243792cc3603ab","tid":1952721,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:37:51.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"d7724e73c663b72ce9775f9e84b9d5f6b1a1f899","tid":1952721,"uid":2962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:39:01.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d480eb42c4e85bf741b36f6ad13f9c9266f9fcd5","tid":1952721,"uid":2962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:44:46.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c8120ffe4df94d6842f93bf47d02074717b5efa9","tid":1952721,"uid":290205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:45:52.000Z","msg":"P牌空氣一推...."},{"pid":"9e0fd8eeb25f884a1330a68e2031f67ca6aa6bc9","tid":1952721,"uid":92500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T18:47:04.